snippet.title: Fans want #JusticeForJohnnyDepp after Amber Heard allegedly ADMITS hitting him
snippet.description:
The battle between exes Johnny Depp and Amber Heard has been making headlines for quite some time. New information was just released in audio shared by Depp's side from a 2015 therapy session. Among other things, Amber allegedly can be heard admitting she hit Depp. Watch the video to know more!
